                                                    <a name="post21958" href="/web/20110322194758/http://www.wonderfulwaterloo.com/showthread.php/932-Waterloo-s-Rental-Licensing-Bylaw?s=f6cd0b0f1073cba408cb794eb002a963&amp;p=21958#post21958" class="postcounter">#1</a><a id="postcount21958" name="1"></a>
                                            
                                            
                                            
