    </div>
     No one likes slum landlors, and those aren't the one this will punish.  Slum landlords don't follow the rules now, why will they follow new rules?  We need more enforcement for slum landlords, and we need to not punish owners who play by the rules.<br />
    <br />
    PS the Council meeting tonight is at 6:30 and you're all invited to come <img src="/web/20110322194758im_/http://www.wonderfulwaterloo.com/images/smilies/Package1/RpS_thumbup.gif" border="0" alt="" title="RpS Thumbup" class="inlineimg" />
